{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "link4deal-auth-collection",
    "name": "Link4Deal — Auth y rutas protegidas",
    "description": "Colección para probar login JWT por rol y acceder a las APIs protegidas.\n\n**Antes de usar:**\n1. Importa también `Link4Deal-Local.postman_environment.json` y actívalo.\n2. Crea usuarios demo: `node server/scripts/seed-demo-dashboard-users.js --apply`\n3. Super admin (opcional): `node server/scripts/promote-user-to-super-admin.js`\n4. Ejecuta la carpeta **01 — Login (todos los roles)** con *Run collection* o cada request por separado.\n\n**Roles demo:** usuario, influencer, brand, agency (`DemoLink4Deal2026!`).\n**Super admin:** `email_superadmin` + `superAdminPassword` (ver script promote-user-to-super-admin.js).\n\nLas rutas SPA (`/admin`, `/dashboard`, etc.) requieren navegador; esta colección cubre las APIs `/api/...`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 — Setup",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "API info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "01 — Login (todos los roles)",
      "description": "Ejecuta estos requests para guardar tokens en el entorno (`token_usuario`, `token_influencer`, etc.).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login — Usuario (user)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Login usuario OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token_usuario', body.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body.refreshToken) pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "if (body.user?.id) pm.environment.set('userId', body.user.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"{{email_usuario}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Influencer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Login influencer OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token_influencer', body.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body.refreshToken) pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "if (body.user?.id) pm.environment.set('userId', body.user.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"{{email_influencer}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Marca (brand)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Login brand OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token_brand', body.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body.refreshToken) pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "if (body.user?.id) pm.environment.set('userId', body.user.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"{{email_brand}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Agencia (agency)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Login agency OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token_agency', body.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body.refreshToken) pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "if (body.user?.id) pm.environment.set('userId', body.user.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"{{email_agency}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Super Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Login super admin OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token_superadmin', body.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', body.token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (body.refreshToken) pm.environment.set('refreshToken', body.refreshToken);",
                  "if (body.user?.id) pm.environment.set('userId', body.user.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"{{email_superadmin}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{superAdminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — App Influencer (auth dedicado)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('App influencer login OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const token = body.token || body.data?.token;",
                  "if (token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token_influencer', token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', token);",
                  "}",
                  "const inf = body.influencer || body.data?.influencer;",
                  "if (inf?._id) pm.environment.set('influencerId', inf._id);",
                  "if (inf?.id) pm.environment.set('influencerId', inf.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"login\": \"{{email_influencer}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{demoPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/app/auth/login"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 — Sesión (Bearer {{token}})",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/auth/me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/refresh",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "03 — Usuario (token_usuario)",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token_usuario}}", "type": "string" }]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/auth/me",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me" }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/users/:id (propio perfil)",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "04 — Influencer (token_influencer)",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token_influencer}}", "type": "string" }]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Perfil y cuenta",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "GET /api/influencers/me",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "const b = pm.response.json();",
                      "const inf = b.influencer || b.data?.influencer || b;",
                      "const id = inf?._id || inf?.id;",
                      "if (id) pm.environment.set('influencerId', id);"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/me" }
            },
            {
              "name": "GET /api/influencers/me/edit-access",
              "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/me/edit-access" }
            },
            {
              "name": "GET /api/influencers/messages/inbox",
              "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/messages/inbox" }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "App móvil influencer",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "POST /api/influencers/app/verify-session",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/app/verify-session"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "GET /api/influencers/app/campaigns",
              "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/app/campaigns" }
            },
            {
              "name": "GET /api/influencers/app/settlements/summary",
              "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/app/settlements/summary" }
            },
            {
              "name": "GET /api/influencers/app/settlements",
              "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/app/settlements" }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Tráfico y analytics",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "GET /api/influencers/:id/traffic-stats",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/influencers/{{influencerId}}/traffic-stats"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
