    {
      "name": "12 — Referencia rutas SPA protegidas",
      "description": "Rutas del frontend (React). Abrir en navegador con sesión iniciada; Postman no las sirve directamente.\n\n| Rol | Rutas principales |\n|-----|-------------------|\n| Usuario | `/marketplace`, `/dashboard` (solo superuser) |\n| Influencer | `/influencer`, `/influencer/panel`, `/influencer/setup`, `/influencer/{{influencerSlug}}` |\n| Marca | `/brands`, `/brands/panel`, `/brands/setup`, `/brands/aplicaciones` |\n| Agencia | `/agency`, `/agency/setup` |\n| Super admin | `/admin`, `/admin/dashboard`, `/admin/crm`, `/admin/influencers`, `/admin/brands`, `/admin/agencies`, `/dashboard/suite` |\n\nTras login web, el JWT se guarda en localStorage del navegador (no en Postman).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "(info) Abrir frontend — Influencer hub",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{frontendUrl}}/influencer"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "(info) Abrir frontend — Admin CRM",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{frontendUrl}}/admin/crm"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "(info) Abrir frontend — Dashboard suite",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{frontendUrl}}/dashboard/suite"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
